@1011  = ~Minor Spell Deflection
Level: 3
School: Abjuration
Range: Personal
Duration: 5 turns
Casting Time: 3
Area of Effect: Caster
Saving Throw: None

This abjuration spell causes any spells cast against the wizard to be absorbed and consumed. This affects a total of 7 spell levels, but even having 1 level of protection left means a 9th-level spell would get absorbed, as well as a 1st-level spell. This spell will protect the caster from Dispel Magic and Breach as long as but the Deflection lasts.
