@1061  = ~Spell Thrust
Level: 3
School: Abjuration
Range: Long
Duration: Instant
Casting Time: 3
Area of Effect: 15' radius
Saving Throw: None

When this spell is cast it will attempt to break one spell protection in effect around the target. It will eliminate 8 levels of absorption from Minor Spell Deflection, Spell Deflection, or Greater Spell Deflection the Deflection (thus utterly destroying the Minor variant). If the target is protected by Spell Shield, this spell will destroy the Spell Shield instead. Spell Thrust will also dispel Dispelling Screen or Non-Detection if the target or targets are not protected by Spell Deflection or Spell Shield.

The target's magic resistance, if any, does not affect this spell.
~
